html:
My dad actually forwarded this to me recently, and it seems somewhat in line with what we're trying to do here at ToS;DR. I'd like to see what people think about it, so if you have time (it's not very long), give it a read and post a response here.

Here's the link: http://www.thenation.com/blog/173362/small-print-big-problem-part-ii-remedies#

Ian

--
